subject: Track and Field
Olympic Games (2012)
Olympic Games
lead_paragraph: Allyson Felix and Jeneba Tarmoh qualified for the semifinals in the women’s 200 meters on Thursday, moving them one step closer to resolving their dead heat for third place in the 100 meters.
